Stash
=====

Stash is a modified version (a "fork") of Dime, an open-source iOS
personal-finance tracker.

Original work
-------------
  Dime
  Copyright (C) 2022 Rafael Soh
  Source: https://github.com/rafsoh/dimeApp

Modifications
-------------
  Stash
  Modifications Copyright (C) 2026 Habib Allawati

  Stash re-brands and extends Dime. Changes include (but are not limited
  to) the application name and identity, bundle identifiers, App Group and
  iCloud container namespaces (com.habibm96.stash), and various UI and
  feature changes. Modified source files carry a "Modified by" note in
  their header; see the project's git history for the full record of
  changes and their dates.

